data.name: 8. Confirm payment & update status (Order Status Update)

labels: 8. Confirm payment & update status (Order Status Update)

threats.title: Order Data Tampering
threats.description: Attacker modifies order details in transit to alter quantities, prices, or products.
threats.mitigation: Implement data validation, checksums, and secure transport protocols (TLS).

threats.title: Payment Data Interception
threats.description: Attacker captures sensitive payment details during transmission.
threats.mitigation: Implement TLS 1.3, field-level encryption, and PCI DSS compliant data handling.

threats.title: Man-in-the-Browser Attack
threats.description: Malware modifies payment details before transmission to the server.
threats.mitigation: Implement client-side integrity checks, fraud detection based on behavior analysis.
